title: Dalai Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Western, Juice bar, Asian, Fusion
description: Vegetarian restaurant at the Shanti Angkor Center, located behind Borei Pram Prei, on the west road to Angkor Wat, set in a garden. Serves vegetarian and vegan food, selection of tea and fresh juices and shakes. At the Center is also a shop selling literature, eco style clothing, tea collections, decorations made of natural stones, charms and mental souvenirs in the style of New Age.
streetAddress: Trapaing Ses Village, Kuk Choh Commune
